{"per_page":10,"total":16,"current":16,"data":[{"title":"centOS 7 下firewalld防火墙基本命令的使用","date":"2018-04-19T01:56:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-firewalld-的基本使用\">1.firewalld 的基本使用<a href=\"post/35#1-firewalld-的基本使用\"></a></h1><p>一下命令是在root用户下使用，如果不是请加sudo<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">启动：systemctl start firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">状态：systemctl status firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">关闭：systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">暂停：systemctl disable firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">重启:systemctl restart firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/35","tags":["firewalld","permanent","systemctl","tcp","zone","命令"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":" linux （centos 7）ps命令查看应用程序进程号、端口","date":"2018-04-19T00:55:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-查看xxx进程对应的进程号\">1.查看xxx进程对应的进程号<a href=\"post/34#1-查看xxx进程对应的进程号\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ps aux | grep xxx</span><br><span class=\"line\">ps -ef | grep xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"1-1-ps-aux、ps-aux、ps-ef之间的区别\">1.1 ps aux、ps -aux、ps -ef之间的区别<a href=\"post/34#1-1-ps-aux、ps-aux、ps-ef之间的区别\"></a></h2><p>Linux中的ps命令是Process Status的缩写。ps命令用来列出系统中当前运行的那些进程。ps命令列出的是当前那些进程的快照，就是执行ps命令的那个时刻的那些进程，如果想要动态的显示进程信息，就可以使用top命令。<br>具体参数可以参考man ps或<br><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/peida/archive/2012/12/19/2824418.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.cnblogs.com/peida/archive/2012/12/19/2824418.html</a><br></p>","link":"post/34","tags":["aux","grep","命令","显示","进程"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"ssm框架中dao层如何调用数据库中数据spring配置——个人小总结","date":"2018-04-13T01:39:00.000Z","excerpt":"<ol>\n<li>propertyConfigurer读取dbconfig数据库连接信息，通过<code>org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer</code> 将dbcongfig的信息返回给<code>阿里 druid数据库连接池</code><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;bean id=&quot;propertyConfigurer&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;property name=&quot;locations&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;list&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;value&gt;/WEB-INF/classes/dbconfig.properties&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/list&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>","link":"post/30","tags":["dao","daosupport","obj","str","数据库"],"categories":["Spring"]},{"title":"linux设置开机启动 systemctl enable","date":"2018-04-09T03:13:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"是超级用户权限下\">是超级用户权限下<a href=\"post/25#是超级用户权限下\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable //这句话的意思就是将那个服务设置开机启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable httpd //设置开机启动httpd服务</span><br><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable php-fpm //设置php开机启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/25","tags":["enable","php","php-fpm","systemctl","开机"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"在linux中查看mysql数据库中表","date":"2018-04-03T05:10:00.000Z","excerpt":"<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql -uroot -p //进入数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">show databases; //查看musql中数据库列表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">use dataname; //选择数据库名</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">show tables; // 查看数据库中的所有表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">describe tablename; //查看表结构</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">最后对表进行sql语句操作</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/16","tags":["知识点"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"一小步","date":"2018-04-03T02:45:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/11","tags":["心情"],"categories":["Life"]}]}